data.description: WOW! Beautiful historic Spanish style property built in 1928.Freshly painted exterior.Excellent location in downtown Lake Worth. Three bedroom with den, formal dining room, and living room. Could also be used for a home based business. Hardwood floors, Coquina fireplace, 9.5 ft. cove ceilings, and a Florida room. Minutes from 95 and the beach. A short stroll to Lake Avenue restaurants and entertainment district.Use Code  0101 - SINGLE FAMILY-COMM ZONINGZoning MU-FH - Mixed Use Federal Hwy ( 38-LAKE WORTH )
